                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant G</hi> 10.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 30th March, 1846; and con<lb></lb>fined one month</hi>)—I was present—the prisoner is the person.</p>
